transcripts: This is the Breville electric Wok. The only electric wok of its kind. It can actually sear steak, beef, fish, up to 425 degrees Fahrenheit. It's also got this 14 settings on the side so you can actually do pastas eggs anything in it and it's dishwasher safe so that makes it easy. It's got this non stick quantanium surface which is also dishwasher safe but the great Innovation is the butterfly element. Now with this one you can see the butterfly shape here and what that means is that heat travels up the sides of the rim so you're getting even consistent results every time. Another great Innovation by Breville.
